sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as 用户
    participant FE as 前端控制台
    participant SC as SyncController
    participant SJS as SyncJobService
    participant OBC as OneBoundReviewClient
    participant OB as OneBound API
    participant SJR as SyncJobRepository
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    User->>FE: 触发开始同步
    FE->>SC: POST /api/v1/sync/start
    SC->>SJS: createJob(provider, platform, targetProductCode)
    SJS->>SJS: 归一化 provider/platform
    SJS->>SJS: 初始化 QUEUED 响应

    alt provider = onebound
        SJS->>OBC: fetchFirstPageReviewCount(platform, targetProductCode)
        OBC->>OB: 请求 /{platform}/item_review
        OB-->>OBC: 评论数据或错误
        alt 请求成功
            OBC-->>SJS: 返回第一页评论数
            SJS->>SJS: 组装 SUCCEEDED 响应
        else 请求失败
            OBC-->>SJS: 抛出异常
            SJS->>SJS: 组装 FAILED 响应并脱敏错误信息
        end
    else provider ≠ onebound
        SJS->>SJS: 保持 QUEUED，不发起真实同步
    end

    SJS->>SJR: create(response, finishedAt)
    SJR->>DB: 写入 sync_jobs
    DB-->>SJR: 返回 jobId
    SJR-->>SJS: SyncJobResponse
    SJS-->>SC: SyncJobResponse
    SC-->>FE: 202 Accepted + job 数据
    FE-->>User: 展示同步结果
